name: WE HAVE re-ISSUES - PART 1-THE FURGUSONS
description:
The Furguson’s was created in 1993 when driven down fell apart, the name came from our friend "Skins" it was Al Bundys dream toilet and we had all been kicked out of bands for crappy reasons so that’s how we got the name. Mike from drunk in public recorded us in my garage for some beer and a 9 song demo was created from a drunken BBQ

Transferred from the old demo tape to MP3 format. It was EQ'ed and compressed a little to make it sound a little better.

name: Johnny Cock And The Nuts/Public Defecation-Up Split Creek Vol 1
description: The first of the up split creek series. Two bands with two completely different styles. 10 songs by Johnny Cock and the Nuts, raw and obnoxious in your face punk, most songs unreleased until this split. 7 originals and 3 covers(Motorhead,Meatmen,RKL). 9 songs by Public Defecation they lean towards the political side of things but maintain a sense of humor.

name: 107 Miles Of Noise
description: A 21 band compilation featuring local bands from the area in between San Luis Obispo and Santa Barbara California. Tracks by damaged Goods, Dead Set Against, Wimpy Dicks, Derita Sisters, S.P.& C, Hot Carl And The Chilli Dogs, The Deveros, Johnny Cock And The Nuts ,Cruel Romeos, Brigands, Countless Shadows, Dead A Week Later, Rat Pack (yes the same one on nardcore), Undisputed , Public Defecation, Gutterfish, Drunk In Public , Weapon A, A Human And His Std’s, The Kilz , The Last Call. A great mix of what the area has to offer.
